{"title":"老农走进田间","authors":["高金光"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":6,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老农走进田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高金光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小南风一吹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦穗就黄过遥远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴草帽的老农"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将毒辣的日头撇在云端"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他走进责任田里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑眯了双眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搓净的麦粒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在粗壮的手心里晶亮滚圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像他播种时滴下的汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时才冒出香甜"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}